quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  8,9,"(Rangarirai) apo pamakakumbira rubatsiro kuna Tenzi venyu, uye vakakupindurai vachiti: “Ndichakubatsirai nechiuru chengirozi dzichiteverana.”"
  8,10,"Allah vakaita kuti rive rombo rakanaka, uye kuti moyo yenyu ive inozorora naro. Uye hakuna kukunda kunze kwekuti kuchibva kuna Allah. Zvirokwazvo, Allah ndivo samasimba, vane hungwaru hwese"
  8,11,"(Rangarirai) apo vakaita kuti murare (kubatwa nehope) sechengetedzo kubva kwavari, uye vakakutumirai mvura kubva kudenga kuti ikuchenurei, uye igobvisa hutsvina hwaDhiyabhorosi mukati menyu, uye kusimbisa moyo yenyu, uye kusimbisa makumbo enyu"
  8,12,"(Rangarira) apo Tenzi vako vakaudza ngirozi (kuti): “Zvirokwazvo ndinemi, nokudaro simbisai vatendi. Ndichaisa kutya mumoyo yevasingatendi, nokudaro damburai huro pamwe nezvigunwe zvavo.”"
  8,13,"Izvi ndizvo nokuda kwekuti vaipikisa Allah nemutumwa wavo (SAW). Uye uyo anopikisa Allah nemutumwa wavo (SAW), zvirokwazvo, Allah vane mutongo unorwadza"
  8,14,"Uyu ndiwo (mutongo), nokudaro uravirei; uye nekuti zvirokwazvo vasingatendi vachawana mutongo weGehena"
  8,15,"Imi vatendi! Pamunosangana neavo vasingatendi, muhondo, musafuratire (kutiza)"
  8,16,"Uye uyo anofuratira kubva kwavari muzuva iri, kunze kwekuti uri hurongwa hwehondo, kana kudzoka kune vamwe vake (mauto), zvirokwazvo anenge azviunzira kutsamwa kwaAllah. Uye musha wake iGehena, uye zvirokwazvo ndiwo magumo akaipa"